      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical release-controlled; FDA in-house code under version control with unit-test suite; DePuy Synthes solver validated per ISO 9001 QMS. All three pass Gradation 2 SQA requirements.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA environments (FDA research code, Ansys 2022 R2, DePuy Synthes proprietary solver) operate under documented version-control and change-management procedures consistent with Gradation 2 SQA. Regression test suites executed prior to each analysis run; no anomalies recorded."
