      "rationale": "Three-level mesh convergence study performed on the pedicle screw-rod-vertebral body assembly. Stiffness QoI changed by 1.4% between medium and fine meshes. Richardson extrapolation estimated discretization error of 0.9% for the fine mesh, well within the 2% acceptance threshold."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
